
sample_lifecycle: Set device lifecycle

The container can be run in TESTED or PROVISIONED or MISSION lifecycle.

To run (load and start) container:
$ mwtest.py -c100 run sample_lifecycle.img

Send command to set lifecycle to PROVISIONED:
$ printf "\01\00\00\00" > testfile
$ cmtest data -f100 testfile

To unload container:
$ mwtest.py -c100 unload
